room_title: Escape room "The Great Outdoors" by North Valley Escape Room in Phoenix
room_address: 42302 N Vision Way, Suite 104, Anthem, AZ 85086
room_description: The ghosts of Fall Mountain have returned and taken over the campground. You and your team have been hired by the park service to reclaim the campground for the living and seal away the ghosts for all eternity. Do you have what it takes? If not, you may just become another ghost of Fall Mountain!
